// This is an express js project which provides api for booking tickets
// to use the apis, you'll need to first sign up if you haven't yet.
// then log in with the same credentials..
// If you are using Postman, an access token will be given to you to add to your headers.
// Afterwards you can continue to use the rest of the apis-- you'd have been authorized to use them after following the steps above.

// for your credentials, this is the structure you need to input
// {
// name:'john doe',
// email:'johndoe@email.com',
// password: 'some password'
// }

// for booking a ticket, this is the structure to input
// {
// id: 1,
// passenger: 'john doe',
// flight: "your flight no."
// }
